prettymux (0.2.0-1) jammy; urgency=medium

  * Port from Qt6/Chromium to GTK4/WebKitGTK
  * Modular C codebase (ghostty_terminal, browser_tab, workspace, etc.)
  * Native tab drag-and-drop with notebook groups (Chrome-like visuals)
  * Embedded web inspector below browser tab
  * Command palette with type badges and monospace search
  * Shortcuts overlay with pill key badges and search filter
  * Desktop notifications via notify-send
  * prettymux-open CLI tool with full IPC command API
  * Session save/restore with CWD per tab
  * Focus-on-hover for terminal panes
  * Activity indicators, progress bars, notification bell
  * Port scanning, git branch detection, broadcast mode
  * Thread-safe ghostty action callback (marshaled to main thread)

 -- patcito <patcito@gmail.com>  Sun, 30 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
